metadata.name: Checks - Ordinals: 4876/80
metadata.description: The 80 skittles Check 4876 is the world's first Check Original from Jack Butcher's Visualize Value art project to be permanently inscribed on the Bitcoin blockchain.  This NFT commemorates the event and may enable holders to participate meaningfully in the fate of both or either the ordinal and Check 4876.  Mint price memes the SATS cost of minting the ordinal.
